&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a detail-oriented and proactive Analyst to support Tamara’s campaign management and collections vendor reporting. Responsible for developing and optimizing multi-channel collections campaigns to improve customer engagement, payment conversion, and overall digital collection performance. The role also oversees collection agency governance, reporting, and compliance, ensuring adherence to regulatory requirements and internal policies while partnering with internal teams and external vendors to drive operational excellence and customer outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
