&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tamara is the leading fintech platform in Saudi Arabia and the wider GCC region with a mission to help people make their dreams come true by building the most customer-centric financial super-app on earth. The company serves millions of users in the region and partners with leading global and regional brands such as SHEIN, Jarir, noon, IKEA and Amazon, as well as small and medium businesses.&lt;/p&gt;
