&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly analytical and technically proficient &lt;strong&gt;Credit Risk Data Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; to support our Portfolio Oversight team. In this role, you will be responsible for managing the health and performance of the credit portfolio. You will not only build the &quot;Single Source of Truth&quot; for risk data but also translate complex datasets into actionable strategies for underwriting, limit management, and loss forecasting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
