&lt;li&gt;Investigate suspicious activities and prepare detailed reports of findings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with other teams to implement fraud prevention measures and improve overall security.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up-to-date with industry trends and developments in fraud prevention techniques and technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
