&lt;li&gt;Support fraud risk assessments, testing activities, and follow-ups on identified issues or control enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to maintaining fraud policies and procedures, ensuring consistency and operational clarity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Fraud Operations to validate case resolutions, identify recurring patterns, and propose control improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
